name: You Want This, Don't You?
Lore: '''I can feel the hate swelling in you now...''',
Text: 'Deploy on table. Once per turn may place a card from hand here (lost if Effect canceled). If Luke''s Lightsaber on table, its gametext is canceled and opponent''s battle destiny draws are -X, where X = number of cards here. Opponent may lose 2 Force to cancel Effect.',
